Dengê Cûdî, the voice of the Rojava revolution has been silenced due to technical problems. They need $10K in order to go back on air. We want to help them.
---
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SSEzy9PhxPw

@altvid: ${data_prefix}uploads/videos/denge-cudi.mp4

<p>Denge Cudi was the first radio of the Rojava revolution. It went through great difficulties to keep spreading the voice of the youth and women. It to offered to many the possibility to express what they were going through and connect all those living in Rojava.</p>

<p>Today this radio can't broadcast anymore because their transmitter is burned. To help them to be back on air. Check out the <a href="https://wemakeit.com/projects/support-radio-denge-cudi" target="_blank">fundraising campaign</a>, where you can also find out how to contact them personaly.</p>

